<para><computeroutput>string KTN::Feeds::CME::connection::id</computeroutput></para>
<para>Connections are identified by an id, which is comprised of: Channel (i.e. &quot;310&quot;), FeedTypeIndicator &#8211; a combination of FeedType (&quot;Incremental&quot;) and Feed (&quot;A&quot; or &quot;B&quot;),</para>

<para>So, the Incremental A connection for channel 310 would be: &quot;310IA&quot; </para>
